title: Coast To Coast AM 04 21 2014 Chinese Lunar Images
description:
Hour 2, 3 and half of 4 only sorry I messed up recording it, for those who cant wait for cashsale's full show
Former NASA consultant and science adviser to CBS News and Walter Cronkite, Richard C. Hoagland, will reveal "history-changing" results of the recent four-month-old Chinese Chang'e-3 unmanned landing on the Moon. Hoagland will present --with startling Chinese government lunar images-- "what the Chinese have really discovered on the Moon." In addition, he'll update several science stories, including the state of current private space explorations, and NASA
